data.name: BXTELECOM
data.notes:
BXTELECOM is a research & development network that makes the network more accessible.

We have an open peering policy you can ask to peer with us by sending an email to noc@bxtelecom.eu

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Informations: 
Used protocols: 
 - OSPF for internal routes 
 - iBGP for the interconnection of my routers
 - eBGP for peering & IP transit 
 - L2TP for DSL Access 

Used Hardware:
 - Mikrotik CCR 1036 
 - Mikrotik CCR 1072
 - Server with VyOS 
 - Juniper MX 80
 - Switch Cisco Nexus 3064-PQ
 - HP Proliant 360 G10 with proxmox for hypervisor
